/// Classify a [`PathFdError`] into a human-readable reason.
///
/// `PathFd::new()` wraps `open(path, O_PATH | O_CLOEXEC)` which can fail for
/// several reasons beyond simple non-existence. The `PathFdError::OpenCall`
